選舉就用咁既手段</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果加泰獨立到 又有錢既話就會有另一種講法<br />\n<br />\n我覺得歐洲會重演納粹 不過呢次係屠伊斯蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">申請國還必須承認歐盟已經存在的法律，並得到已經存在的成員國同意。</span><br />\n有呢條例係到<br />\n咁西班牙自己一定唔比加泰獨立<br />\n歐盟其他人真係做唔到其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢條例原意應該係防俄佬反吞歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893d04e3950617b7daae259ba49a5643dc454e8a","tid":419203,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"加泰同英國組聯盟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴塞踢英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c99134eab31ce7e6499d298165e7e385210c43","tid":419203,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:59:57.000Z","msg":"歐盟加入一向就有套程序要行架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8376b30669e58fa3398518cdebd30c6635322725","tid":419203,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又見識到歐盟左膠係幾咁虛偽<br />\n對住伊斯蘭豬就話要包容<br />\n對住實實在在民主投票既選舉就用咁既手段</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果加泰獨立到 又有錢既話就會有另一種講法<br />\n<br />\n我覺得歐洲會重演納粹 不過呢次係屠伊斯蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">申請國還必須承認歐盟已經存在的法律，並得到已經存在的成員國同意。</span><br />\n有呢條例係到<br />\n咁西班牙自己一定唔比加泰獨立<br />\n歐盟其他人真係做唔到其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢條例原意應該係防俄佬反吞歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該未必係<br />\n歐盟搞呢條例最主要應該係本身歐洲國家都有唔少活躍分離主義<br />\n佢唔打正旗號反對呢樣野<br />\n咁你話堆會員國會唔會怕歐盟有一日俾分離主義借黎做外力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3061a22a2bc070f6700c48e506860c73e736e275","tid":419203,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"歐盟中意攬住西班牙一齊死都無辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef36a829fc6ebd52aa12c19228f89c4e2b72bc21","tid":419203,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:17:20.000Z","msg":"其實所有爭取獨立國家應該爭取聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1845b8d724ce2a82e8176a9ceff56a018065ec56","tid":419203,"uid":66714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:23:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實所有爭取獨立國家應該爭取聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%84%A1%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%8C%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%258F%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594&d=P9li7PRKRRlwFvomZPFEwzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ab3da419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%84%A1%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%8C%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94</a><br />\n<br />\n小聯合國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10442d59e975ed8b6bc72c57eeea34a61f2c636","tid":419203,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:28:54.000Z","msg":"痴埋英國佬到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歐盟真係好撚7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解d歐洲佬成日都係咁，由二戰希特拉想征服歐洲，到而家歐盟個目的又係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098c7dcd81cdd4c7c9a7f7499a09f25da6fe7805","tid":419203,"u